-- main.bi_output.bi_ouput_v_dim_instrumenttype (VIEW, 2 columns)
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.bi_ouput_v_dim_instrumenttype.`InstrumentTypeID` IS 'Instrument type category: 1=Currencies (forex), 2=Commodities, 4=Indices, 5=Stocks, 6=ETF, 10=Crypto Currencies. Note TypeIDs 3, 7, 8, 9 are unused gaps. Distribution: Stocks 82%, ETF 8%, Crypto 4%, Commodities 3%, Indices 2%, Currencies 1%. (Tier 2 -- SP_Dim_Instrument)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.bi_ouput_v_dim_instrumenttype.`InstrumentType` IS 'Text label for InstrumentTypeID -- DWH-computed via CASE: 1=Currencies, 2=Commodities, 4=Indices, 5=Stocks, 6=ETF, 10=Crypto Currencies, else=Other. Use InstrumentTypeID for filtering; InstrumentType for display. (Tier 2 -- SP_Dim_Instrument)';

-- main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie (VIEW, 46 columns)
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`CID` IS 'Customer ID. Identifies the eToro customer who made this deposit. References DWH_dbo.Dim_Customer. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`CurrencyID` IS 'Currency of the deposit amount. References DWH_dbo.Dim_Currency. 1=USD, 2=EUR, 3=GBP, etc. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`Commission` IS 'Commission charged on this deposit. Default 0 in production. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`Approved` IS 'Legacy approval flag, superseded by PaymentStatusID=2. NULL for most modern records. Retained for backward compatibility. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ModificationDate` IS 'UTC timestamp of the most recent modification to this deposit record. Used by ETL for incremental detection. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ModificationDateID` IS 'ETL key. Integer YYYYMMDD derived from ModificationDate (CONVERT(INT, date)). Used for rolling-window DELETE+INSERT. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`FundingID` IS 'Payment instrument (credit card, bank account, e-wallet) used for this deposit. References Billing.Funding. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ExchangeRate` IS 'Exchange rate from deposit currency to USD at processing time. Cannot be 0 in production. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`DepositID` IS 'Primary distribution key (HASH). Uniquely identifies each deposit attempt. PK in production (Billing.Deposit.DepositID IDENTITY). Clustered index key in DWH. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ProcessorValueDate` IS 'Value date from the payment processor. Mandatory for offline/wire deposits. NULL for instant payment methods. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`DepotID` IS 'Acquirer/gateway configuration used for this deposit. Validated at insert against DepotToCurrency in production. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`PaymentStatusID` IS 'Current deposit status. Key values: 1=New, 2=Approved (73%), 3=Decline, 5=InProcess, 11=Chargeback, 12=Refund, 13=Pending, 35=DeclineByRRE (10.2%). Full 39-value enum in upstream wiki. NC index key. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ManagerID` IS 'Operations manager who processed this deposit. 0=automated. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`RiskManagementStatusID` IS 'Result of the pre-processing risk management check. 69 distinct risk reason codes. NULL=no risk check recorded. Key codes: 1=Success, 35=DeclineByRRE, 47=ML, 49=CustomerToFundingViolation. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`Amount` IS 'Deposit amount in the deposit currency (CurrencyID). As of 2025-04-17, capped via CASE expression in ETL to prevent extreme outlier values from distorting aggregations. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`PaymentDate` IS 'UTC timestamp when the deposit was submitted (set at INSERT in production). Not the approval time. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IPAddress` IS 'Customer IP address at deposit time, as a 32-bit integer. Used for fraud detection. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ClearingHouseEffectiveDate` IS 'Settlement date assigned by the clearing house. NULL for instant payment methods. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IsFTD` IS 'First Time Deposit flag. 1=this was the customer''s very first approved deposit (drives marketing attribution). 0=repeat deposit or ineligible type. ~60.6% of deposits are FTD=1 in Billing.Deposit. Stored as int in DWH (vs. bit in production). (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`RefundVerificationCode` IS 'Verification code for refund correlation. Set by UpdateRefundDetails. NULL for non-refunded deposits. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`MatchStatusID` IS 'PSP reconciliation match status. Default 0=Unmatched; 3=Matched. Used for provider reconciliation workflows. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`BonusStatusID` IS 'Promotional bonus status. Values: 0=New, 1=Approved, 2=Declined, 3=Reverted. Only 239 non-zero records in production. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`BonusAmount` IS 'Bonus amount credited with this deposit. NULL when no bonus applies. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`BonusErrorCode` IS 'Error code when bonus processing fails (BonusStatusID=2). NULL when bonus succeeds or not attempted. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ExTransactionID` IS 'External (payment provider) transaction ID. Used for provider-side reconciliation and dispute resolution. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`FundingTypeID` IS 'Type of payment instrument. Sourced from Billing.Funding.FundingTypeID (not from Billing.Deposit directly). Categorizes the deposit by payment method (credit card, wire, ACH, etc.). (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IsRefundExcluded` IS 'Whether this deposit is excluded from refund eligibility. Sourced from Billing.Funding.IsRefundExcluded. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`DocumentRequired` IS 'Whether documentation was required for this deposit/funding instrument. Sourced from Billing.Funding.DocumentRequired. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ExpirationDateID` IS 'Integer date ID derived from ExpirationDateAsString XML attribute via a complex formula in SP. Represents card expiration date as YYYYMMDD. NC index key. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`BaseExchangeRate` IS 'Reference exchange rate before fee markup. Fee spread = ExchangeRate - BaseExchangeRate. Added by Adi (19/09/2019). (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ExchangeFee` IS 'Exchange fee in provider-specific integer encoding (basis points). Added by Adi (19/02/2019). (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ProtocolMIDSettingsID` IS 'Merchant ID configuration profile. Default 0=no specific MID. Added 2018-10-24. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`FunnelID` IS 'Marketing funnel ID. FK to Dictionary.Funnel. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`AmountUSD` IS 'Deposit amount converted to USD. DWH-computed: Amount × ExchangeRate. Not from production source - pre-computed in ETL for reporting convenience. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`SessionID` IS 'Application session ID. Used for PlatformID enrichment via Fact_CustomerAction JOIN (second ETL pass). (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`PlatformID` IS 'Device/platform the customer used for this deposit. NOT from Billing.Deposit - enriched via second ETL pass: JOIN Fact_CustomerAction ON SessionID WHERE ActionTypeID=14. NULL if no matching session action found. References DWH_dbo.Dim_Platform. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`PaymentGeneration` IS 'Payment infrastructure generation: 0=Gen0 (7.7%), 1=Gen1 (92%). Added 2020-04-19. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`ProcessRegulationID` IS 'Regulatory entity/jurisdiction: 1=Cyprus/EU (~63%), 2=UK/FCA (~16%), 4=AU (~2.5%), others for ASIC etc. Added DBA-646, 2021-09-05. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`MerchantAccountID` IS 'Merchant account legal entity for regulatory routing. Added with DBA-646. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IsSetBalanceCompleted` IS '1=account crediting (Billing.AmountAdd) completed for this deposit. Added DBA-646. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`RoutingReasonID` IS 'Reason code for routing path selection. Values 1-8; 3=most common (~29%). ~31% NULL for legacy records. Added PAYUS-3061, 2021-06-15. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IsRecurring` IS '1=deposit is part of a recurring schedule (OUTER APPLY on Billing.RecurringDeposit). 0=one-time deposit. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`FlowID` IS 'Deposit UX flow variant. NULL=default (98.9%), 1=new flow (0.97%), 3=specific variant. Added PAYIL-8362, 2024-04-18. (Tier 1 - upstream wiki, Billing.Deposit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IsAftSupportedAsBool` IS 'Whether Account Funding Transaction (AFT) is supported by this funding instrument. Sourced from Billing.Funding. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IsAftEligibleAsBool` IS 'Whether this deposit was eligible for AFT processing. Sourced from Billing.Funding. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingdeposit_for_genie.`IsAftProcessedAsBool` IS 'Whether this deposit was actually processed via AFT. Sourced from Billing.Funding or Billing.Deposit. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingDeposit_DL_To_Synapse)';

-- main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie (VIEW, 18 columns)
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`CID` IS 'Customer ID. FK to Customer.CustomerStatic. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`WithdrawID` IS 'Withdrawal request identifier. Primary key, IDENTITY starting at 1. HASH distribution key and clustered index column. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`FundingID` IS 'FK to Billing.Funding - the payment instrument to which the withdrawal is paid. NULL if no specific instrument selected. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`Amount_Withdraw` IS 'Gross withdrawal amount in CurrencyID denomination. Renamed from Amount to disambiguate from WithdrawToFunding Amount. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`ExchangeRate` IS 'Exchange rate applied to convert from withdrawal currency to ProcessCurrencyID. NULL for same-currency payouts. (Tier 1 - Billing.WithdrawToFunding)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`BaseExchangeRate` IS 'Reference exchange rate before fee markup. Spread = ExchangeRate minus BaseExchangeRate. (Tier 1 - Billing.WithdrawToFunding)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`Fee` IS 'Platform fee charged for this withdrawal. Subtracted from the gross Amount_Withdraw. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`CashoutStatusID_Withdraw` IS 'Withdrawal request-level status. FK to Dim_CashoutStatus. 10 distinct values: 1=Pending, 2=InProcess, 3=Processed, 4=Cancelled. Renamed from CashoutStatusID. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`CashoutReasonID` IS 'Internal reason code for the withdrawal decision (e.g., why cancelled or flagged). FK to Dim_CashoutReason. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`ErrorCodeAsString` IS 'Provider error code if the payment leg failed or was rejected. Extracted from wtf.WithdrawData XML only. NULL for successful transactions. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingWithdraw_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`ResponseMessageAsString` IS 'Provider response message (success/failure details). Extracted from wtf.WithdrawData XML only. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingWithdraw_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`ModificationDate` IS 'UTC timestamp of the most recent status change or update on the withdrawal request. (Tier 1 - Billing.Withdraw)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`BankNameAsString` IS 'Bank name from the bf.FundingData XML. Distinct from the enriched BankName (#82) which comes from Dim_CountryBin BIN-code lookup, and ClientBankNameAsString (#44) which is COALESCE from wtf/bf. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingWithdraw_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`ProtocolMIDSettingsID` IS 'MID configuration profile used for this payment leg. FK to Dim_BillingProtocolMIDSettingsID. Default=0. (Tier 1 - Billing.WithdrawToFunding)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`BinCodeAsString` IS 'Bank Identification Number (first 6-8 digits of card). COALESCE from wtf/bf XML. CAST to INT for JOIN with Dim_CountryBin to populate BankName and CardCategory. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingWithdraw_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`BinCountryIDAsInteger` IS 'Country associated with the BIN code. COALESCE from wtf/bf XML. FK to Dim_Country after CAST to INT. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingWithdraw_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`CardTypeIDAsInteger` IS 'Card type identifier (Visa, Mastercard, etc.). COALESCE from wtf/bf XML. FK to Dim_CardType after CAST to INT. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingWithdraw_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_billingwithdraw_for_genie.`CardCategory` IS 'Card category (Debit, Credit, Prepaid, etc.) looked up from BIN code via post-load enrichment JOIN to Dim_CountryBin.CardCategory. NULL when BIN code not found. (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_BillingWithdraw)';

-- main.bi_output.vg_fact_snapshotcustomer_for_emoney_genie (VIEW, 1 columns)
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output.vg_fact_snapshotcustomer_for_emoney_genie.`GCID` IS 'Global Customer ID - the cross-platform identifier linking RealCID to demo and external systems. Source: Ext_FSC_Real_Customer_Customer (primary), Ext_Dim_Customer_CustomerIdentification_DLT (fallback). (Tier 2 - SP_Fact_SnapshotCustomer)';

-- main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_2_vw_dim_customer (VIEW, 3 columns)
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_2_vw_dim_customer.`GCID` IS 'Group Customer ID - cross-product identity key linking the same person across eToro products/entities. NULL for older accounts predating GCID introduction. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_2_vw_dim_customer.`FirstDepositDate` IS 'Date of first deposit. DEFAULT=''19000101''. Updated from CustomerFinanceDB FTD data with FTDRecoveryDate logic. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_2_vw_dim_customer.`FirstDepositAmount` IS 'Amount of first deposit (in USD). Updated from FTDAmountInUsd. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';

-- main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer (VIEW, 106 columns)
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`GCID` IS 'Group Customer ID - cross-product identity key linking the same person across eToro products/entities. NULL for older accounts predating GCID introduction. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RealCID` IS 'Customer ID - platform-internal primary key. Assigned at registration. Unique within etoro DB. Used as the universal customer identifier across all tables. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`DemoCID` IS 'Demo account CID associated with this customer. From `UserApiDB_Customer_CustomerIdentification`. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`OriginalCID` IS 'Original customer ID from the source provider. Together with OriginalProviderID, enables tracing of migrated accounts. Default=0. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`UserName` IS 'Customer login username. Unique (case-insensitive, enforced via UserName_LOWER computed column index). (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FirstName` IS 'Legal first name in Unicode. nvarchar supports non-Latin scripts (Cyrillic, Arabic, etc.). Used in LinkedAccountHash1. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`LastName` IS 'Legal last name in Unicode. Used in LinkedAccountHash1. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`Gender` IS 'Gender: M, F, or U (Unknown). CHECK constraint CCST_GENDER enforces these three values only. Used in LinkedAccountHash1. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`BirthDate` IS 'Customer date of birth. Used in LinkedAccountHash1 for duplicate detection and in KYC age verification. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`ReferralID` IS 'Referral CID - the customer who referred this customer (for RAF program tracking). (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`CountryID` IS 'Country of residence. FK to Dictionary.Country. Determines regulatory framework, available instruments, and leverage limits. Default=0. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IP` IS 'Registration IP address. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`AffiliateID` IS 'Affiliate (partner) ID under which the customer was acquired (renamed from SerialID). FK to BackOffice.Affiliate. NULL for direct/organic registrations. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`CampaignID` IS 'Marketing campaign ID under which the customer was acquired. FK to BackOffice.Campaign. NULL for organically acquired customers. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`SubChannelID` IS 'Sub-channel ID. Populated post-load from SubChannel unify code via AffiliateID mapping. DEFAULT=0. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`LabelID` IS 'Internal segment label. FK to Dictionary.Label. LabelID=26 = BonusOnly customer (triggers IsHedged=0). Default=0. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`LanguageID` IS 'Customer preferred platform language. FK to Dictionary.Language. Controls UI language. Default=0. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`Email` IS 'Customer email address. Unique (case-insensitive via LowerEmail computed column). Email changes trigger Customer.LastChanges update via trigger. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`Phone` IS 'Phone number from production Customer.CustomerStatic. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`Zip` IS 'Postal code. Used in LinkedAccountHash1. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`City` IS 'City in Unicode. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`Address` IS 'Street address in Unicode. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`AccountExpirationDate` IS 'Expiration date for demo or time-limited accounts. NULL for standard real-money accounts. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`SocialConnectID` IS 'Social media connection type. DEFAULT=0. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`VerificationLevelID` IS 'KYC verification level. FK to Dictionary.VerificationLevel. Values: 0=unverified (34.2%), 1=partial (12.4%), 2=intermediate (6.2%), 3=fully verified (47.1%). Default=0. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`DocsOK` IS 'Whether required documents are verified. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PlayerStatusID` IS 'Compliance and trading account status. FK to Dictionary.PlayerStatus. 1=Active/Registered (97.5% of accounts); other values indicate restricted, closed, banned, or special states. Default=0. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`Bankruptcy` IS 'Bankruptcy flag. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FunnelID` IS 'Registration funnel ID. FK to Dictionary.Funnel. Tracks which user journey/funnel variant the customer came through. NULL when not tracked. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`DownloadID` IS 'Platform download source ID. Legacy tracking for which platform installer the customer used. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RegisteredReal` IS 'Account registration date (renamed from Registered). Default=getdate(). (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RegisteredDemo` IS 'Demo account registration date. Source unclear - may be populated separately. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FunnelFromID` IS 'Source funnel variant ID tracking where the customer came from within the acquisition funnel. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RiskStatusID` IS 'Legacy single-value risk status. Distinct from the multi-row BackOffice.CustomerRisk (which allows multiple simultaneous risk flags). (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RiskClassificationID` IS 'Operational risk tier assigned by risk management. FK to Dictionary.RiskClassification. Tracked in UPDATE trigger audit. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`EmployeeAccount` IS '1 if this is an eToro employee personal trading account (renamed from isEmployeeAccount). Flags employee accounts for special monitoring and compliance checks. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`CommunicationLanguageID` IS 'Language for customer communications (emails, notifications). May differ from LanguageID if customer has different communication preferences. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`BannerID` IS 'Advertising banner ID that led to registration. Legacy acquisition tracking. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PremiumAccount` IS 'Whether this is a premium account. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`Evangelist` IS 'Whether this customer is an evangelist/ambassador. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`GuruStatusID` IS 'eToro Popular Investor/Guru program status - whether the customer is an active copy trading strategy provider. FK to Dictionary.GuruStatus. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`NumOfGurus` IS 'Number of Popular Investors this customer is copying. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`NumOfCopiers` IS 'Number of customers copying this customer''s trades. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`NumOfRAF` IS 'Number of successful Refer-A-Friend referrals. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`AccountTypeID` IS 'Customer account classification. Default=1 (real retail account). Distribution: 1=18.614M, 0=44K, 2=37K, 6=17K, others <6K. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RegulationID` IS 'Regulatory entity governing this account. FK to Dictionary.Regulation. Top values: CySEC=7.39M, BVI=7.30M, FCA=1.17M. Changes trigger RegulationChangeDate update. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PlayerLevelID` IS 'Customer experience/permission level. FK to Dictionary.PlayerLevel. 1=Standard (94%); 4=Popular Investor; 7=VIP. Determines available features and risk limits. Default=0. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`AccountStatusID` IS 'Account operational status. Default=1 (Active/Normal). 2=Closed or Restricted. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`AccountManagerID` IS 'Currently assigned BackOffice sales/service agent (renamed from ManagerID). FK to BackOffice.Manager. NULL = unassigned. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`HasAvatar` IS 'Whether customer has uploaded a custom avatar. Updated post-load from Avatars staging (excludes default/avatoros images). (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`AvatarUploadDate` IS 'When the avatar was uploaded. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsDepositor` IS 'Whether the customer has ever deposited. DEFAULT=0. Updated post-load from FTD data. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FirstDepositDate` IS 'Date of first deposit. DEFAULT=''19000101''. Updated from CustomerFinanceDB FTD data with FTDRecoveryDate logic. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`ID` IS 'System GUID for REST API identity. Default=newsequentialid() (sequential for index performance). (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`ExternalID` IS 'APEX broker external ID. Decimal(38,0) to accommodate APEX very large numeric ID format. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PlayerStatusReasonID` IS 'Reason code for current PlayerStatusID. Provides the why behind a non-Active status. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PendingClosureStatusID` IS 'Status in the pending closure workflow. Default=1 (no pending closure). Updated when customer requests account closure. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`CountryIDByIP` IS 'Country detected from the customer IP address at registration. Used for fraud detection and geo-comparison (CountryID vs CountryIDByIP mismatch flagging). (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`SubSerialID` IS 'Sub-affiliate identifier string. Can be up to 1024 chars for complex affiliate tracking paths. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`EvMatchStatus` IS 'Electronic verification match result. Score or decision from automated identity verification vendors (Onfido, Au10tix). NULL if not yet processed. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`DocumentStatusID` IS 'Current state of the customer KYC document submission and review queue. NULL if no documents submitted. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RegulationChangeDate` IS 'Timestamp when RegulationID was last changed. Updated automatically by the CustomerHistoryUpdate trigger. NULL if never changed since creation. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsCopyBlocked` IS '1 if the customer is blocked from copy trading. 0 in all current rows - feature exists but currently unused/not enforced. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`WorldCheckID` IS 'Refinitiv/LSEG World-Check sanctions and PEP screening result. FK to Dictionary.WorldCheck. Default=0. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsEDD` IS 'Enhanced Due Diligence required flag. 1 = customer requires deeper AML/KYC investigation (PEP, high-risk country, large transactions). 23,944 customers (0.13%) flagged. Default=0. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`SuitabilityTestStatusID` IS 'MiFID II appropriateness/suitability test result. NULL if test not completed. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FirstDepositAmount` IS 'Amount of first deposit (in USD). Updated from FTDAmountInUsd. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PrivacyPolicyID` IS 'Version of the privacy policy the customer has accepted. FK to Dictionary.PrivacyPolicy. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`MifidCategorizationID` IS 'MiFID II investor classification. FK to Dictionary.MifidCategorization. Values: 1=Retail (97.3%), 4=Eligible Counterparty (2.6%), 5=Professional (0.03%). Default=1. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsEmailVerified` IS 'Whether the email address has been verified by clicking a confirmation link. NULL for older accounts predating this flag. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsValidCustomer` IS 'DWH-computed: 1 when not Popular Investor (PlayerLevelID != 4), not label 30/26, and not CountryID=250. Used in reporting to filter out non-standard customers. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`2FA` IS 'Two-factor authentication status. 0=disabled, 1=enabled. Derived from `STS_Audit_UserOperationsData` login type events. Preserves previous value when no new 2FA event exists. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`DesignatedRegulationID` IS 'Secondary/override regulation for accounts subject to multiple jurisdictions. FK to Dictionary.Regulation. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RegionByIP_ID` IS 'Region detected from IP address. Separate from RegionID (profile-based) to allow mismatch detection. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`ScreeningStatusID` IS 'Compliance screening status. Updated from ScreeningService. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`RegionID` IS 'Geographic region ID (GeoIP-derived or set). Used alongside CountryID for more granular regional regulation. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`WorldCheckResultsUpdated` IS 'When World-Check results were last updated. Preserved from previous row. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`HasWallet` IS '1 if the customer has an active eToro Money wallet linked to their trading account. Default=0. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsAddressProof` IS 'Whether address proof document is on file (1/0). Updated from BackOffice.CustomerDocument. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsAddressProofExpiryDate` IS 'Expiry date of address proof document. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsIDProof` IS 'Whether ID proof document is on file (1/0). (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsIDProofExpiryDate` IS 'Expiry date of ID proof document. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PhoneVerifiedID` IS 'Result code of phone number verification process. NULL if not yet attempted. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`CitizenshipCountryID` IS 'Country of citizenship (may differ from CountryID/residence). FK to Dictionary.Country. Added 2018 for enhanced KYC. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PlayerStatusSubReasonID` IS 'Sub-reason code for PlayerStatus (hierarchical). FK to Dictionary.PlayerStatusSubReasons. Added 2022 (COINF-1989). (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsCreditReportValidCB` IS 'DWH-computed: similar to IsValidCustomer but with additional AccountTypeID != 2 exclusion and specific CID exceptions for CountryID=250. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`CashoutFeeGroupID` IS 'Determines which withdrawal fee schedule applies to this customer. FK to Dictionary.CashoutFeeGroup. NULL = default fee group. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`MiddleName` IS 'Middle name in Unicode. Added 2018. Included in CustomerVersionUpdate history tracking. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`BuildingNumber` IS 'Building/apartment number. Separate from Address for structured address storage. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`UserName_Lower` IS 'Lowercase version of UserName. Set by final UPDATE in SP_Dim_Customer. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`SalesForceAccountID` IS 'Salesforce CRM Account record ID (18-char Salesforce ID). Links the trading account to the SF Account. NULL if not yet synced. (Tier 1 - BackOffice.Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`POBCountryID` IS 'Place of birth country. FK to Dictionary.Country. Added for KYC (HLD: RD-4436). (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`ApexID` IS 'APEX US stocks broker account ID. Only populated for US-regulated customers at Level >= 2 who have APEX accounts. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PhoneNumber` IS 'Verified phone number from ContactVerification service. Overrides `Phone` from Customer_Customer when available. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`IsPhoneVerified` IS 'Whether phone is verified (VerificationStatusID IN (1,2) -> 1). (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`PhoneVerificationDate` IS 'Date phone was verified. ''1900-01-01'' if not verified. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`WeekendFeePrecentage` IS 'Weekend swap fee percentage. Default=100 (full fee). Values below 100 indicate discounted weekend fees for select customers. Note: column name has typo Precentage. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`TanganyID` IS 'Tangany crypto custody integration ID. Updated from CustomerIdentification. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`TanganyStatusID` IS 'Tangany integration status. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`EquiLendID` IS 'EquiLend securities lending integration ID. Updated from StocksLending. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`StocksLendingStatusID` IS 'Stocks lending consent status. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`DltID` IS 'Distributed Ledger Technology integration ID. Updated from CustomerIdentification. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`DltStatusID` IS 'DLT integration status. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FTDPlatformID` IS 'Platform/account type of the first deposit (AccountTypeId from source). Added 2025-09-12. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FTDTransactionID` IS 'Transaction ID of the first deposit (TransactionId from source). Added 2025-09-12. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.bi_output_stg.customer_radar_view_dim_customer.`FTDRecoveryDate` IS 'Recovery date for the FTD (Updated field from source). If FTDRecoveryDate is later than original FirstDepositDate, FirstDepositDate is updated to FTDRecoveryDate. Added 2025-09-12. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Customer)';

