COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`DemoCID` IS 'Demo-account Customer ID. Always 0 in this table (real accounts only). (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`Occurred` IS 'UTC timestamp when the action occurred. For position opens: when position was opened. For logins: login time. For credits: when the credit was recorded. (Tier 1 - source-dependent)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IPNumber` IS 'IP address of the customer as a numeric value. Populated for logins and registrations. (Tier 1 - STS/Billing.Login)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsReal` IS 'Account type flag. Always 1 in this table (real accounts only). (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`ActionTypeID` IS 'Event type classifier. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_ActionType.ActionTypeID` - JOIN for Name, Category, CategoryID. See Section 2.1 for full mapping. Key filter column - drives which other columns are populated. (Tier 1 - ETL-derived from CreditTypeID/source)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`PlatformTypeID` IS 'Legacy platform type. 0=default (most rows), 99=STS source. Values 1-9 for specific platforms. (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`InstrumentID` IS 'FK to Trade.Instrument. Financial instrument being traded. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`Amount` IS 'Position size in currency. Must be >= 0. Stored in dollars (PositionOpen divides by 100 from cents). (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
