COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`NetProfit` IS 'Realized PnL. 0 when open; set on close. In position currency. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`Commission` IS 'Open commission in dollars. PositionOpen stores @Commission/100 (cents to dollars). (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`PositionID` IS 'Primary key. Allocated by Internal.GetPositionID_Bigint. Unique per position. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`CampaignID` IS 'Marketing campaign identifier. 0 if not campaign-related. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_Campaign.CampaignID` - JOIN for Code, Description, StartDate, EndDate, MaxBonusAmount, IsActive. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`BonusTypeID` IS 'Bonus type for bonus events (ActionTypeID=9). 0 for non-bonus events. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_BonusType.BonusTypeID` - JOIN for Name, IsWithdrawable, IsActive. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`FundingTypeID` IS 'Payment method used for deposits/withdrawals. 0 for non-deposit events. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_FundingType.FundingTypeID` - JOIN for Name, IsNewStyle, IsSingleFunding, IsCashoutActive. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`LoginID` IS 'Login session identifier from `Billing.Login`. 0 for non-login events. (Tier 1 - Billing.Login)';
