COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`DurationInSeconds` IS 'Duration of a login session in seconds. NULL for non-login events. (Tier 1 - Billing.Login)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`PostID` IS 'Social post/comment GUID for social engagement events (ActionTypeID 21-26). NULL for non-social events. (Tier 1 - Social platform)';
