COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`DateID` IS 'Date of the action as integer YYYYMMDD. Derived from `Occurred`. Part of nonclustered indexes. (Tier 2 - ETL-computed)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`TimeID` IS 'Hour of the action (0-23). Derived from `DATEPART(HOUR, Occurred)`. (Tier 2 - ETL-computed)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`StatusID` IS 'Row status. Nearly always 1 (active). NULL for ~2M rows. (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`PreviousOccurred` IS 'Deprecated/unused column. NULL for most rows - not reliably populated. Do not use. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`CompensationReasonID` IS 'Compensation reason for compensation events (ActionTypeID=36) and position opens (for airdrop identification). References `BackOffice.CompensationReason`. 0 for non-compensation events. (Tier 1 - History.Credit, updated 2025-12-21)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`WithdrawPaymentID` IS 'Payment processing ID for cashout/withdrawal events. 0 for non-cashout events. Used to deduplicate WithdrawProcessingID rows in the ETL. (Tier 1 - History.Credit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`CommissionOnClose` IS 'Commission charged on close. DWH note: adjusted by SP_Dim_Position when position is reopened; CommissionOnCloseOrig stores the pre-adjustment value. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsPlug` IS 'Deprecated/unused column. Always NULL. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`DepositID` IS 'Deposit transaction identifier. NULL for non-deposit events. (Tier 1 - History.Credit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`PostRootID` IS 'Root post ID for social engagement events. NULL for non-social events. (Tier 1 - Social platform)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`FullCommission` IS 'Full commission including spread. PositionOpen stores @FullCommission/100. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`FullCommissionOnClose` IS 'Full commission on close. DWH note: adjusted by SP_Dim_Position when position is reopened; FullCommissionOnCloseOrig stores the pre-adjustment value. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`RedeemID` IS 'Billing.Redeem reference when position closed via redeem. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`RedeemStatus` IS 'Redemption state. Billing.Redeem integration. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`SessionID` IS 'STS session identifier for logins and position opens. For manual opens: from login session. For copy opens: from mirror session. NULL for other events. (Tier 1 - STS)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsRedeem` IS 'Redeem flag. 0=not a redeem, 1=is a redeem. NULL for non-position events. Same meaning as `Dim_Position.IsRedeem` (via RedeemStatus mapping). (Tier 3 - ETL-derived)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`RegulationIDOnOpen` IS 'Regulatory jurisdiction ID at time of position open. ETL-computed via JOIN to etoro_History_BackOfficeCustomer (customer''s regulation history). ISNULL(..., 0) when no regulation match found. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`PlatformID` IS 'Product/platform identifier - badly named, actually references `Dim_Product.ProductID` (not a standalone platform enum). Resolves to Product, Platform, and SubPlatform via JOIN to `DWH_dbo.Dim_Product`. Only populated for ActionTypeID=14 (logins) and 41 (registrations). (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`ReopenForPositionID` IS 'When position was reopened: references the erroneously closed PositionID. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsReOpen` IS '1=this position was reopened from ReopenForPositionID. ETL-computed: CASE WHEN ReopenForPositionID IS NOT NULL THEN 1. Default 0. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`CommissionOnCloseOrig` IS 'Original CommissionOnClose before reopen adjustments. ETL: CASE WHEN ReopenForPositionID IS NOT NULL THEN CommissionOnClose ELSE 0. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`FullCommissionOnCloseOrig` IS 'Original FullCommissionOnClose before reopen. ETL default 0. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`OriginalPositionID` IS 'Original position ID for positions split by partial close. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsPartialCloseParent` IS '1=this position was partially closed (is the parent in a partial close event). (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsPartialCloseChild` IS '1=this position is the child (remainder) of a partial close event. Generally filter out child positions from most metrics on OPEN when aggregating, but not all (e.g., volume is already pro-rated so excluding these is wrong). NEVER filter these out on CLOSE. (Tier 5 — domain expert, SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`InitialUnits` IS 'Original unit count at open. Used for partial close ratio. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`PaymentStatusID` IS 'Payment processing status for deposit/cashout events. NULL for non-payment events. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_PaymentStatus.PaymentStatusID` - JOIN for Name. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsDiscounted` IS '1=position received a discounted rate. DWH note: CAST from bit to int. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsSettled` IS '1 = real asset, 0 = CFD asset. (Tier 5 - Expert Review)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`CommissionByUnits` IS 'Prorated commission for partial close. Formula: (AmountInUnitsDecimal / InitialUnits) * Commission. Used for partial-close PnL. (Tier 1 - Trade.Position)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`FullCommissionByUnits` IS 'Prorated full commission for partial close. Same proration formula as CommissionByUnits applied to FullCommission. (Tier 1 - Trade.Position)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsFTD` IS 'First-Time Deposit flag: 1 = this is the customer''s first deposit. NULL for non-deposit events. (Tier 2 - ETL-computed)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`CountryIDByIP` IS 'Country determined by IP geolocation. Populated for logins and registrations. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_Country.CountryID` - JOIN for country name. Also see `DWH_dbo.Dim_CountryIP` for IP-to-country resolution. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsAnonymousIP` IS 'Anonymous IP flag: 1 = connection via anonymous proxy/VPN. NULL for most rows. (Tier 1 - IP geolocation)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`ProxyType` IS 'Proxy classification: DCH=datacenter, VPN=VPN, PUB=public proxy, SES=session proxy, TOR=Tor exit node, WEB=web proxy. NULL for non-proxy connections. (Tier 1 - STS)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsFeeDividend` IS 'Fee sub-type for ActionTypeID=35: 1=overnight/weekend fee, 2=dividend, 3=SDRT, 4=ticket fees (OpenTotalFees/CloseTotalFees). NULL for non-fee events. See Section 2.2 and DSM-1463. (Tier 2 - ETL-derived from Description)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsAirDrop` IS '1=position was created via an airdrop event (crypto). ETL-computed: JOIN to etoro_Trade_PositionAirdropLog. NULL=not an airdrop. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`DividendID` IS 'Dividend event identifier for dividend-related fees. NULL for non-dividend events. (Tier 1 - Trade positions)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`MoveMoneyReasonID` IS 'Reason for money movement: 1=Adjustment, 5=InternalTransfer Trade, 6=InternalTransfer, 8=Recurring Deposit, 9=Recurring Investment. References `Dictionary.MoveMoneyReason`. (Tier 1 - History.Credit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`SettlementTypeID` IS 'Modern settlement classification. Dictionary.SettlementTypes: 0=CFD, 1=REAL, 2=TRS, 3=CMT, 4=REAL_FUTURES, 5=MARGIN_TRADE. Replaces IsSettled. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`DLTOpen` IS 'DLT flag at open. Added 2024-06-02 (Ofir A). (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`DLTClose` IS 'DLT flag at close. Added 2024-06-02. NULL for open positions and older positions. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`OpenMarkupByUnits` IS 'Prorated open markup for partial close. Formula: OpenMarkup * AmountInUnitsDecimal / InitialUnits. (Tier 1 - Trade.Position)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`Description` IS 'Human-readable description. Populated mainly for ActionTypeID=35 (fees): "Over night fee", "Payment caused by dividend", "Weekend fee", "OpenTotalFees", "CloseTotalFees", "SDRT Charge". For ActionTypeID=32: "edit stop loss by customer". For deposits: "Processed By eToro.Payments.Deposit", etc. (Tier 1 - History.Credit, added 2024-08)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`IsBuy` IS '1 = Long/Buy (profit when price rises), 0 = Short/Sell. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep.v_fact_customeraction_enriched.`CreditID` IS 'Reference to the source `History.Credit.CreditID`. Enables join back to credit history for audit. (Tier 1 - History.Credit, added 2025-07)';

-- main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics (VIEW, 70 columns)
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`HistoryID` IS 'Intended as a unique key but contains duplicates - NOT reliable as a primary/unique identifier. Do not use for JOINs, deduplication, or row identification. Has no practical use for analysts. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`GCID` IS 'Global Customer ID - the platform-wide unique customer identifier. References `Dim_Customer.GCID`. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`RealCID` IS 'Real-account Customer ID. HASH distribution key. References `Dim_Customer.RealCID`. Each customer has one real CID. (Tier 1 - Customer.CustomerStatic)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`DemoCID` IS 'Demo-account Customer ID. Always 0 in this table (real accounts only). (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`Occurred` IS 'UTC timestamp when the action occurred. For position opens: when position was opened. For logins: login time. For credits: when the credit was recorded. (Tier 1 - source-dependent)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`IPNumber` IS 'IP address of the customer as a numeric value. Populated for logins and registrations. (Tier 1 - STS/Billing.Login)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`IsReal` IS 'Account type flag. Always 1 in this table (real accounts only). (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`ActionTypeID` IS 'Event type classifier. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_ActionType.ActionTypeID` - JOIN for Name, Category, CategoryID. See Section 2.1 for full mapping. Key filter column - drives which other columns are populated. (Tier 1 - ETL-derived from CreditTypeID/source)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`PlatformTypeID` IS 'Legacy platform type. 0=default (most rows), 99=STS source. Values 1-9 for specific platforms. (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`InstrumentID` IS 'FK to Trade.Instrument. Financial instrument being traded. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`Amount` IS 'Position size in currency. Must be >= 0. Stored in dollars (PositionOpen divides by 100 from cents). (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`Leverage` IS 'Leverage multiplier (1, 5, 10, etc.). Determines margin and settlement type. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`NetProfit` IS 'Realized PnL. 0 when open; set on close. In position currency. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`Commission` IS 'Open commission in dollars. PositionOpen stores @Commission/100 (cents to dollars). (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`PositionID` IS 'Primary key. Allocated by Internal.GetPositionID_Bigint. Unique per position. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`CampaignID` IS 'Marketing campaign identifier. 0 if not campaign-related. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_Campaign.CampaignID` - JOIN for Code, Description, StartDate, EndDate, MaxBonusAmount, IsActive. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`BonusTypeID` IS 'Bonus type for bonus events (ActionTypeID=9). 0 for non-bonus events. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_BonusType.BonusTypeID` - JOIN for Name, IsWithdrawable, IsActive. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`FundingTypeID` IS 'Payment method used for deposits/withdrawals. 0 for non-deposit events. References `DWH_dbo.Dim_FundingType.FundingTypeID` - JOIN for Name, IsNewStyle, IsSingleFunding, IsCashoutActive. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`LoginID` IS 'Login session identifier from `Billing.Login`. 0 for non-login events. (Tier 1 - Billing.Login)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`MirrorID` IS 'FK to Trade.Mirror. 0/NULL = manual. Positive = copy-trade position. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`WithdrawID` IS 'Withdrawal request ID for cashout events. 0 for non-cashout events. (Tier 1 - History.Credit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`DurationInSeconds` IS 'Duration of a login session in seconds. NULL for non-login events. (Tier 1 - Billing.Login)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`PostID` IS 'Social post/comment GUID for social engagement events (ActionTypeID 21-26). NULL for non-social events. (Tier 1 - Social platform)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`CaseID` IS 'CRM case identifier for ActionTypeID=31 (Open CRM Case). 0 otherwise. (Tier 1 - CRM)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`DateID` IS 'Date of the action as integer YYYYMMDD. Derived from `Occurred`. Part of nonclustered indexes. (Tier 2 - ETL-computed)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`TimeID` IS 'Hour of the action (0-23). Derived from `DATEPART(HOUR, Occurred)`. (Tier 2 - ETL-computed)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`StatusID` IS 'Row status. Nearly always 1 (active). NULL for ~2M rows. (Tier 3 - ETL-assigned)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`PreviousOccurred` IS 'Deprecated/unused column. NULL for most rows - not reliably populated. Do not use. (Tier 5 - domain expert)';
