COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`IsAnonymousIP` IS 'Anonymous IP flag: 1 = connection via anonymous proxy/VPN. NULL for most rows. (Tier 1 - IP geolocation)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`ProxyType` IS 'Proxy classification: DCH=datacenter, VPN=VPN, PUB=public proxy, SES=session proxy, TOR=Tor exit node, WEB=web proxy. NULL for non-proxy connections. (Tier 1 - STS)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`IsFeeDividend` IS 'Fee sub-type for ActionTypeID=35: 1=overnight/weekend fee, 2=dividend, 3=SDRT, 4=ticket fees (OpenTotalFees/CloseTotalFees). NULL for non-fee events. See Section 2.2 and DSM-1463. (Tier 2 - ETL-derived from Description)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`IsAirDrop` IS '1=position was created via an airdrop event (crypto). ETL-computed: JOIN to etoro_Trade_PositionAirdropLog. NULL=not an airdrop. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`DividendID` IS 'Dividend event identifier for dividend-related fees. NULL for non-dividend events. (Tier 1 - Trade positions)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`MoveMoneyReasonID` IS 'Reason for money movement: 1=Adjustment, 5=InternalTransfer Trade, 6=InternalTransfer, 8=Recurring Deposit, 9=Recurring Investment. References `Dictionary.MoveMoneyReason`. (Tier 1 - History.Credit)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`SettlementTypeID` IS 'Modern settlement classification. Dictionary.SettlementTypes: 0=CFD, 1=REAL, 2=TRS, 3=CMT, 4=REAL_FUTURES, 5=MARGIN_TRADE. Replaces IsSettled. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`DLTOpen` IS 'DLT flag at open. Added 2024-06-02 (Ofir A). (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`DLTClose` IS 'DLT flag at close. Added 2024-06-02. NULL for open positions and older positions. (Tier 2 - SP_Dim_Position_DL_To_Synapse)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`OpenMarkupByUnits` IS 'Prorated open markup for partial close. Formula: OpenMarkup * AmountInUnitsDecimal / InitialUnits. (Tier 1 - Trade.Position)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`Description` IS 'Human-readable description. Populated mainly for ActionTypeID=35 (fees): "Over night fee", "Payment caused by dividend", "Weekend fee", "OpenTotalFees", "CloseTotalFees", "SDRT Charge". For ActionTypeID=32: "edit stop loss by customer". For deposits: "Processed By eToro.Payments.Deposit", etc. (Tier 1 - History.Credit, added 2024-08)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`IsBuy` IS '1 = Long/Buy (profit when price rises), 0 = Short/Sell. (Tier 1 - Trade.PositionTbl)';
COMMENT ON COLUMN main.etoro_kpi_prep_stg.v_fact_customeraction_w_metrics.`CreditID` IS 'Reference to the source `History.Credit.CreditID`. Enables join back to credit history for audit. (Tier 1 - History.Credit, added 2025-07)';

